# New organization classification codes (ticket: new org types).
# prefLabel = technically-correct org name; altLabel = colloquial werkingsgebied term.
# URIs minted under lblod.data.gift (not data.vlaanderen.be/id/concept, to avoid extending the squat).
# Each code is inScheme its family scheme AND the public-export scheme (10caf4a4) = the export switch.
@prefix rdf:    <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix skos:   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> .
@prefix mu:     <http://mu.semte.ch/vocabularies/core/> .
@prefix ext:    <http://mu.semte.ch/vocabularies/ext/> .
@prefix code:   <http://lblod.data.gift/vocabularies/organisatie/> .
@prefix scheme: <http://data.vlaanderen.be/id/conceptscheme/> .

# --- BestuurseenheidClassificatieCode (besluit:Bestuurseenheid) ---

